knowledge.question: In the above Assembly code, what's contained in the rax register when finished?
knowledge.snippet:
1 | mov rax, 2
2 | shr rax, 2
3 | shl rax, 2
4 |
explanation: mov rax, 2 puts ...00000010 into rax, shr (shift right) 2, shifts bits 2 to right resulting in ...00000000 in rax, shl (shift left) 1 shifts all bits one to left but has no affect because register is all zeros
